• Simplified and improved the patient in-take form to make it easier for you to connect a doctor.
• Made it easier for you now to upgrade and transition from text chat to video during a virtual visit with a doctor.
• Enabled the ability for you to now download and share a doctor’s note after completing a virtual visit.

• Unlimited virtual doctor visits for just $119/year. (Less than $10/ month!)
• Hundreds of new, patient-asked, doctor-answered questions about COVID-19/coronavirus that are free to search
• Artificial-intelligence-powered symptom checker trained on flu-like symptoms to assess and triage the likelihood of COVID-19/coronavirus
• Doctors trained daily on the latest protocols for diagnosing, treating, and managing suspected and confirmed COVID-19/coronavirus cases
• Care guidelines refreshed daily with guidance from the Centers for Disease Control (CDC) and the World Health Organization (WHO) on prevention, management, self-quarantine, caregiving for high-risk individuals

Improvements & Fixes:

We are constantly making performance and reliability improvements to make sure you get the information and the care you need, when you need it, for you and your family.
• Bug fixes and performance improvements

• HealthTap is now accepting insurance to cover 24/7 virtual doctor visits! Many plans cover 100% of telemedicine costs.
• No insurance or high-deductible plan? We still offer our affordable monthly membership for 24/7 virtual doctor visits.
Bug fixes and performance improvements

• As a HealthTap Prime subscriber, you can now check to see if you are eligible to use your health insurance for Primary Care appointments. Primary Care available in select states only.
• HealthTap Prime subscribers can also more easily reschedule an upcoming primary care appointment.
• Past appointments now prominently display the status if they were missed, or canceled along with the cancellation reason.
• We redesigned our settings page to make certain sections easier to find. We moved the transactions section to your account page to make it easier for you to view each transaction in detail.
